First Quantum Unit Awarded Mauritanian Gold Exploration Licenses, AMI Says

-- B y   O u d a a   M a r o u f
-- 
2011-05-20T08:38:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-20/first-quantum-unit-awarded-mauritanian-gold-exploration-licenses-ami-says.html
Mauritanian Copper Mines SA, a unit
of  First Quantum Minerals Ltd. (FM) , has been awarded two licenses to
search for gold in  Mauritania ,  AMI reported , citing a statement
from the government.  The permits were part of an award by Mauritania, during
which the government awarded a total of five licenses for gold
and another five for  iron ore , the state-owned  news agency  said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Oudaa Marouf in Nouakchott via Johannesburg at   pmrichardson@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin on  at  asguazzin@bloomberg.net  